Package edu.ncsu.csc216.stp.model.util

Interface ILog<E>

Type Parameters:
E - type for the ILog
All Known Implementing Classes:
Log
public interface ILog<E>
Represents as list where elements can only be added to the end of the list. Once an element is added, it cannot be removed.
Author:
Dr. Sarah Heckman
